description: This is a .NET 6/8 command line app/dotnet tool to run XSLT 3.0 with Saxon 10.9 HE.
releaseNotes: This is the initial release with a dual package for .NET 6 and .NET 8 with the new IKVM 8.10.1/Maven 1.8.0 using the latest build 422 of the Java 8/1.8 JDK
title: .NET 6/8 command line app/dotnet tool to run XSLT 3.0 using Saxon 10.9 HE
